De_Portico - Bomb/Defuse
by Schuzak
9/May/2009

Simple, clean, less visual noise, and fps-friendly DE map.


1, Description

Counter-Terrorists:
	Prevent terrorists from bombing or eliminate them.

Terrorists:
	Blast one of two bombsites.


2, Installation

Just extract .BSP file into the maps folder. All required files (.NAV, radar map, materials etc.) are included in .BSP.


3, Contact

e-mail : admin AT schuzak.jp
Web site : http://www.schuzak.jp
